HEADWORD: Silversmith
<hw>Sil"ver*smith`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One whose
occupation is to manufacture utensils, ornaments, etc., of silver; a
worker in silver.</def>⟦br⟧
